markets.title: Will Trump fire any more commissioners who are only supposed to be fired 'for cause' before Jul 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If President Trump fires any more politically appointed regulators who are appointed to fixed terms (see list below) after March 21, 2025 and before Jul 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: This is exclusive to the Commissioners of: the Federal Trade Commission (FTC); Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC); Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC); Federal Communications Commission (FCC); Board of Governors of the; Federal Reserve System (Federal Reserve Board); National Labor Relations Board (NLRB); Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC); Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC); Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC); and the Federal Election Commission (FEC).
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
